<section class="pres-rate">
  <div class="pres-rate__container">
    <div class="pres-rate__intro">
      <p class="pres-rate__eyebrow">The math that lets us pay 10%</p>
      <h2 class="pres-rate__heading">How the rate actually works.</h2>
      <p class="pres-rate__subhead">It is not magic. It is structure.</p>
    </div>

    <ul class="pres-rate__reasons">
      <li class="pres-rate__reason">
        <span class="pres-rate__reason-title">Scarce coastal land</span>
        <p class="pres-rate__reason-body">
          Outer Banks prices doubled in 9 years, from $311K to $622K. Demand outruns the supply we
          already control.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="pres-rate__reason">
        <span class="pres-rate__reason-title">No fund layer</span>
        <p class="pres-rate__reason-body">
          We are not a REIT. There is no manager fee siphoning yield before it reaches you.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="pres-rate__reason">
        <span class="pres-rate__reason-title">No leverage on the digital side</span>
        <p class="pres-rate__reason-body">
          We hold Bitcoin and Ethereum. We do not trade them. No margin call risk.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="pres-rate__reason">
        <span class="pres-rate__reason-title">Founder-run, not committee-run</span>
        <p class="pres-rate__reason-body">
          Decisions are made by the person whose name is on the door.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pres-rate {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-rate__container {
    max-width: 1024px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .pres-rate__intro {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .pres-rate__eyebrow {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 130%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pres-rate__heading {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    line-height: 120%;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-rate__subhead {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #555555;
    line-height: 150%;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-rate__heading + .pres-rate__subhead {
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }

  .pres-rate__reasons {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .pres-rate__reason {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green-brand);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .pres-rate__reason-title {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 130%;
  }

  .pres-rate__reason-body {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 165%;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-rate__close {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 140%;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {
    .pres-rate__container {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      gap: 48px;
    }

    .pres-rate__intro {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .pres-rate__heading {
      font-size: 2.75rem;
    }

    .pres-rate__reasons {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .pres-rate__close {
      font-size: 26px;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1136px) {
    .pres-rate__container {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
    }

    .pres-rate__heading {
      font-size: 3.25rem;
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1920px) {
    .pres-rate__heading {
      font-size: 3.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
